Package com.composum.ai.backend.base.service.chat

Annotation Type GPTBackendConfiguration

  • public @interface GPTBackendConfiguration
    Configuration for a generic LLM backend used by Composum AI. This configuration is defined via OSGi and allows setting API endpoint, authentication, request settings, and model configurations.
